  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrent we send any message to publish off to gossipsub to be sent to our peers. It can fail if we do not have any peers on a given topic. In this instance we just drop the message. \r\n\r\nIn the case of attestations, we should store these in a temporary cache and try to continue searching for peers for a topic, at least for half an epoch. If we manage to connect to peers on the topic, we can re-send the attestation, but log a warning that we've had to cache the message (as this isn't ideal).\r\n",
